@startuml
title UC03 - View Match List Sequence
actor Visitor
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Match API" as API
participant "Match Service" as Svc
database "DB" as DB
Visitor -> UI : Open match list
UI -> API : GET /matches?filters
API -> Svc : listPublicMatches(filters)
Svc -> DB : query matches by status/time
DB --> Svc : matches
Svc --> API : public match DTOs
API --> UI : 200 OK
UI --> Visitor : Display list
@enduml
